      • getPreferredTermMemberFromIndex

        public static Pair<String,IdStorageKeyPair> getPreferredTermMemberFromIndex(Concept concept,
                                                                            String languageRefSetId)
        Deprecated. - revise API
        Returns with a pair, identifying a preferred term associated with the specified SNOMED CT concept.
        This method may return with null.
        • First value of the pair is the SNOMED CT description ID.
        • Second value of the pair is a pair for identifying the language type reference set member:
          • Language reference set member UUID.
          • Language reference set member CDO ID.

        NOTE: This method should not not be called with dirty CDO view.

        Parameters:
        concept - SNOMED CT concept
        languageRefSetId -
        Returns:
        a pair identifying the preferred term member.

                                             @Nullable

        Build a new child concept. All description will be replicated from the parent concept. No NON IS_A relationship will be copied from the parent concept. One and only IS_A relationship will be created with parent concept destination.

        parentConcept - the parent of the new concept.
        conceptId - the unique ID of the concept. Can be null. If null, then the ID will be generated via the specified editing context.
        parentIds -
        Returns:
        the new concept.

      • delete

        public void delete(SnomedDeletionPlan deletionPlan)
        This functions deletes the objects in the deletionplan from the database. For the sake of acceptable execution speed, the remove(int index) function is used instead of the remove(object). This way, the CDO will not iterate through the large number of data in the resources.
        Parameters:
        deletionPlan - the deletionplan containing all the objects to delete
